'''夜曲Op. 48'''是[[蕭邦|蕭邦]]的一組[[夜曲|夜曲]]作品，於1841年創作並於1842年出版<ref>{{cite book|last=Huneker|first=James G.|title=Chopin : the man and his music|publisher=Dover Publ.|location=New York|year=1966|page=251|isbn=0-486-21687-X|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=MPFwo8BrkqQC&printsec=titlepage|access-date=2014-02-04|archive-date=2020-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200512032310/https://books.google.com/books?id=MPFwo8BrkqQC&printsec=titlepage|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它被獻給Mlle. Laure Duperré。

==Op. 48, No. 1==
{|
|[[File:Chopin_nocturne_op48_1a.png|thumb]]
|[[File:Chopin102-001q.jpg|thumb]]
|}
夜曲'''Op. 48, No. 1'''是[[C小調|C小調]]，4/4拍，[[行板|緩板]]，共77小節。到了第25小節樂曲進入[[C大調|C大調]]的第二部分，比開首略慢（poco più lento），到第49小節回到A段，並標記加倍速度（doppio movimento agitato）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www2.deutschegrammophon.com/special/insights.htms?ID=pollini-nocturnes|title=Maurizio Pollini Plays Chopin's Nocturnes|last=Pollini|first=Maurizio|publisher=[[Deutsche_Grammophon|Deutsche Grammophon]]|accessdate=2009-03-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090430180648/http://www2.deutschegrammophon.com/special/insights.htms?ID=pollini-nocturnes|archivedate=2009-04-30}}</ref>。
{{-}}

==Op. 48, No. 2==
[[File:Chopin_nocturne_op48_2a.png|thumb]]
夜曲'''Op. 48, No. 2'''是[[升F小調|升F小調]]，4/4拍，[[行板|小行板]]，共137小節。到了第57小節速度變得更慢(più lento)和轉為[[降D大調|降D大調]]，到了第101小節回復原來速度和升F小調，但到結尾調性變為[[升F大調|升F大調]]<ref>Friskin (1973), pp. 106-107</ref>。

蕭邦曾指出樂曲第二部分像[[宣敘調|宣敘調]]，情景如“一名暴君下命令，而其他人則求饒”（a tyrant commands, and the other asks for mercy）<ref name="ca1">{{cite book |title=AllMusic Guide to Classical Music |last=Woodstra |first=Chris |coauthors=Brennan, Gerald; Schrott, Allen |year=2005 |publisher=Hal Leonard Corporation |isbn=0-87930-865-6 |page=287 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=n29DHVKhZggC |accessdate=21 March 2009 |archive-date=2020-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200512003643/https://books.google.com/books?id=n29DHVKhZggC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
